Hello once again! Thanks for reading. This is my third SCP, and I am quite proud of it.

I would like to give huge thanks to taylor_itkin, Leveritas, 9Volt, and anyone else who looked at this before I posted.

I own the picture taken (and yes, I did go find a tree, staple bread to it, and take a picture of it).

Also, thanks to Mendelssohn, who brought up christian symbolism when I put a picture of bread stapled to a tree in chat. And thus inspired this article.

